description: Product Description9to5Cables HDMI Cables are premium quality Category 2 Certified cables that help you extract the maximum performance from your home theater or gaming setup so you can enjoy stunning high-definition visuals and surround sound on your HDTV or projector. This cable reproduces dual 1080p Full HD video streams for advanced 3D movies and games.9to5Cables ULTRA series cables are lighter in weight compared to our PREMIUM series cables with same performance standards.9to5Cables - Quality Construction- 3FT - 30 AWG.- Certified to support advanced HDMI features such as 3D, Ethernet and Audio Return.- Hi Quality 24k gold-plated connectors ensure maximum conductivity.- This cable is made of a PVC outer layer that protects from physical strain, external interference & maintains efficiency of the digital signal.Delivers 1080p Video on Amazon FireTV, Roku 3, Apple TV, Google Chromecast and other HDMI Devices- This 9to5cables product offers highest quality for a fraction of the price you'd pay elsewhere for same quality.Supported Features3D4K, 1440p, 1080p, 1080i, 720p, 480p, and 480i ResolutionsAudio ReturnDeep ColorHighest Refresh Rates AvailableTransfer Rates of At Least 10.2GbpsTrue HD Dolby 7.1 and DTS-HD Master AudioHDCP CompliantEthernet Sharing via HDMIBackwards Compatible with All Previous HDMI Standards.Lifetime Warranty9to5Cables Full lifetime warranty means we stand behind our products.
title: 9To5Cables High Speed Ultra HDMI Cable with Ethernet (3 Feet) Full HD - Supports 3D, 1080p and Audio Return [Latest Version] - Delivers 1080p Video on Amazon Fire TV, Roku 3, Apple TV, Google Chromecast and other HDMI Devices
